ahoo.com As soon as possible would someone please add him to the members pa=
ge ASAP)

::Bobertron/Pantron/CyberShark::

    They were heading to the Pr=
edacon base. The locked into CyberShark's signal.
    After a little bit of=
 running. They reached CyberShark.
    "Why are you trying to talk to the P=
reds?" Bobertron asked CyberShark.
    "I am no longer a Destron. I am help=
ing restore order to Cybertron with Volouis, Soundwave, and Battera," Cyber=
Shark said.
    "I don't think so, you can't quit us. We're not the Cybertr=
on Postal Service," Bobertron said.
    CyberShark pulled out a fin blade a=
nd sliced Bobertron's chest. Bobertron was shocked. He pulled out a gun and=
 aimed it at Cyber's head. But before he could even get it up there CyberSh=
ark used the fin to slice it in two peices.
    "Do you really think that y=
ou can defeat me in combat?" CyberShark asked of Bobertron. "Magmatron buil=
t me to be second only to him. There is no way you can destroy me, or force=
 me to return to the base."
    "Maybe we both can." Pantron said as he sho=
t CyberShark in the chest. CyberShark fell back. Bobertron pulled out his s=
econd gun and he and Pantron aimed their weapons at CyberShark. "Goodbye tr=
aitor."
    They fired at CyberShark. But he rolled out of the way and cloa=
ked. Bobertron and Pantron looked around but didn't see any movement. Cyber=
Shark pulled out his gun and set it to target them both. He fired. The miss=
les found their mark.
    Bobertron grabbed Pantron and pulled him away.
  =
  "The Pred autoguns should be coming on soon, CyberShark will be finished =
by them." They high tailed it out of there.
